NAME
    shit - just use stuff

VERSION
    version 0.02

SYNOPSIS
      use shit;

      no shit;

DESCRIPTION
    Enables strict and warnings without all the typing.

    To enable just "use shit" in your script.

    "no shit" disables strict and warnings.

